Connect4

Connect4 is a c++ command line version of the childhood game Connect Four.

To make the game, move into the Connect4 directory and type in the 'make' into the terminal. 
Then to run game, type in './play' in the terminal


The rules of the game are simple:
	Needs 2 players to play
	The first player to get four pieces in a row vertically, horizontally, or diagonally wins.
	

	
